description: Troy's Mobile Outboard Service We offer services including routine maintenance, basic repairs, and prebuyer's inspection. Hourly Rate is $ 85. All labor prices depend on corrosion and accessibility. We charge travel time depending on location. Estimated Labor Rates (per engine) POWERHEAD Annual service, most 2 stroke below 100 HP	$155+ parts Annual service, most 2 stroke 100 hp and up	$185 Annual service, Yamaha Hpdi	$245 Annual service, Mercury Optimax	$245 Annual service, 4 stroke 40hp to 70hp	$185 Annual service, 4 stroke 75,90,115hp	$185 Annual service, 4 stroke IL 150&200 Yamaha	$200 Annual service, 4 stroke V200 and up	$220 NOTE....Gear-case service cannot be performed if vessel is in the water. Gear case service ALL size	$35+ parts+fluid ( oil change&propR&R) Prices are labor only and do not include travel time or parts. We do a complete service for the price. Parts pricing is different depending on manufacture of outboard. The annual service includes, but not limited to, compression test, ignition test, check/adjust linkages, check anodes, check/change spark plugs, replace fuel filters,( except VST, that is an additional charge when it's time for replacement), replace engine oil and filter, change gear oil, grease all zerk fittings, check belts, ( if replacement of timing belt is required, there is added labor time involved), grease prop shaft splines, grease trim/tilt rams, grease transom bracket, spray motor with CRC corrosion protectant. Water pump Service The water pump service is a separate service, do to not always needing a replacement on a yearly bases as other items such as oil changes, if a water pump service is needed, the vessel must be out of the water for accessibility. Arrangements must be made by vessel owner prior to the technician arriving to perform services. Most 2 stroke engines (Except Johnson/Evinrude)	$127+parts Johnson/Evinrude $143+parts All 4 Stroke engines(Except Verado)	$127+parts Verado+oil change $212+parts These are labor prices, this is impeller replacement only, if a full rebuild with new housing is required do to severe melting, there is added labor time in doing the repair plus the parts. We do not service, nor do repairs on inboard/sterndrive engines.....sorry We only offer haul out service for pontoons up to 24 feet, depends on situation..minimum charge$45.00
